   [:header
    [:h1 {:class "page-title"}
     "Commitment to collaboration"]
    [:p {:class "page-description"}]]
   [:div {:class "page-body"}
    [:p {:id "c36382bf-e3d2-498b-a30b-8d3636a086f5"
         :class ""}
     "At Hephaistox, we firmly believe in the value of commitments. As they are crucial for the success of any project. This belief holds even more significance for Supply Chain projects, which are often multi-disciplinary, involving teams that may not be accustomed to working closely together. Therefore a strong commitment is essential to ensure the effectiveness of the collaboration."]
    [:p {:id "a8fe64f3-d94d-400b-b2b8-a50182f9c8ab"
         :class ""}
     "We have described the three following commitments that we will work on with you throughout the various project stages:"]
    [:h2 {:id "3d56dcad-8d31-402a-8454-3eb0e3c3b841"
          :class ""}
     "1. Active Engagement and Collaboration:"]
    [:h3 {:id "c1301a7b-65eb-46be-98ff-39a3e99e32af"
          :class ""}
     "What it entails"]
    [:p {:id "45c52d0a-5bed-4290-99a8-4947b9d5e62a"
         :class ""}
     "We require your entire team ranging from managers to the shop floor to work closely with us and actively participate in the project. At each step of our offer, we’ll provide you with information about the time we need to spend with all the stakeholders."]
    [:figure {:class "block-color-gray_background callout"
              :style {"whiteSpace" "pre-wrap"
                      "display" "flex"}
              :id "d06a3b01-c120-442a-b2a5-7da0fb91f31c"}
     [:div {:style {"fontSize" "1.5em"}}
      [:span {:class "icon"}
       "ℹ️"]]
     [:div {:style {"width" "100%"}}
      "It is not possible to provide an exact estimate in advance. Since we are unfamiliar with your enterprise size, maturity level, knowledge distribution, etc."]]
    [:h3 {:id "7665b5f8-4f99-45fe-b250-30eb4ba84226"
          :class ""}
     "Why it is necessary?"]
    [:p {:id "e5b850ca-71eb-4782-8b8f-904d5058b187"
         :class ""}
     "Your team possesses invaluable insights into your operations and needs. By actively participating in the project, we can gain a comprehensive understanding of your operations and needs. So, we can design solutions that fit your organization best."]
    [:p {:id "6ce1db21-b783-4574-8f67-def802eb6c65"
         :class ""}
     "For software packages, the users are not required during the development of the solution, but it is coming with a cost when you deploy to users, that must adapt their ways to fit the software practices or reject and work around it. Our solutions are tailored for you, but we need to work with your team to adapt our solutions to their day to day."]
    [:h3 {:id "c255b319-ff8f-4bce-8b23-1ae6f2500611"
          :class ""}
     "Implications for you"]
    [:p {:id "f855575b-b89e-415f-b77a-09cd4f685897"
         :class ""}
     "Before each step, we’ll suggest you a list of people required and the amount of time they need to commit:"]
    [:ul {:id "5f9bf969-faa4-4c86-b91c-70e9cb4ad301"
          :class "bulleted-list"}
     [:li {:style {"listStyleType" "disc"}}
      "That list will need to specify people and their key position in terms of knowledge or ability to introduce the change."]]
    [:ul {:id "af65548e-a521-4c04-aa8e-cded15b2857d"
          :class "bulleted-list"}
     [:li {:style {"listStyleType" "disc"}}
      "This list is a negotiation, we will adjust it with you, but we’ll tell you if conditions are not met to start for that step."]]
    [:ul {:id "9b88bde4-726a-43ac-8e10-7a076d0106ff"
          :class "bulleted-list"}
     [:li {:style {"listStyleType" "disc"}}
      "Your management needs to ensure the availability of these individuals."]]
    [:h2 {:id "d2cacc8e-37be-4b10-b644-7eab9f58fef1"
          :class ""}
     "2. Open Data Sharing and Transparency:"]
    [:h3 {:id "4059926a-c88b-4cc1-84cb-0b77f3cebf85"
          :class ""}
     "What it entails"]
    [:p {:id "14dca9a9-8f15-4ea8-a21f-b4853ecb55b9"
         :class ""}
     "We firmly believe that transparency and open data sharing are the keys to success in our collaboration. Data constitutes facts, and we’ll need access to the necessary data, including financial data, history data, future data, detailed data, aggregated data, and so on."]
    [:p {:id "13d667ef-8c26-451e-acf3-a8b046b66ed1"
         :class ""}
     "Identifying the necessary data and its availability will be among our initial steps."]
    [:h3 {:id "a73afd33-031d-4a30-a6af-bacfc4c3e1ce"
          :class ""}
     "Why it is necessary?"]
    [:p {:id "c6952743-d323-40d4-a01e-30e2842be6d2"
         :class ""}
     "It is necessary to gain a deep understanding of your challenges, identify areas for improvement, and design customized solutions that cater to your needs."]
    [:p {:id "c0f96fa1-b737-407d-93e2-b245f556b3c6"
         :class ""}
     "Data doesn’t lie. While it may be challenging to obtain accurate data, if that data exists and is being used it is the reality for people using it and there is something useful to learn about it."]
    [:h3 {:id "c9b5e2be-21c8-401b-b026-f9cdd77e287b"
          :class ""}
     "Implications for you"]
    [:ul {:id "76fbdc62-0263-4dcb-81fa-83d7056a21cf"
          :class "bulleted-list"}
     [:li {:style {"listStyleType" "disc"}}
